  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ある晩、マリオは奇妙な夢を見ます。そこでは、彼が別の世界への扉を開き、前回のクッパとの冒険よりもさらに奇妙なクリーチャーや土地が広がっています。驚くべきことに、翌日、マリオ、ルイージ、キノピオ、そしてプリンセスは、マリオの夢に出てきた世界へと続く洞窟を見つけます。\n\n夢の国「サブコン」は、ワートの悪い呪いによって危機に瀕しています。そこで、マリオたちは世界を救わなければなりません。新しいクリーチャーとの戦いや、たくさんの厄介なサプライズが待ち受けています。\n\n4人のキャラクターから選び、それぞれ異なるスピードとジャンプ能力を持つキャラクターで、パズル、ボス、ボーナスマネー、いつも助けてくれるキノコ、無敵のスター、さらには爆弾や魔法のポーションが詰まった7つのレベルを進んでいきましょう。\n各レベルの後、集めたコインに応じて、ボーナスゲームで追加のライフを獲得することができます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "スーパーマリオブラザーズ2。前作の難易度を上げた続編。毒キノコが登場。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Super Mario Bros. 2, 2D platformer and sequel to Super Mario Bros. (1985), features 4 selectable characters (Mario, Luigi, Princess Peach, Toad) as they navigate the dream world of Subcon to defeat the evil toad king Wart. Super Mario Bros. 2 features different ways interacting with enemies and the world, including an object carrying mechanic and more intricate level designs.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "One evening, Mario had a strange dream. He dreamt of a long, long stairway leading up to a door. As soon as the door opened, he was confronted with a world he had never seen before spreading out as far as his eyes could see. When he strained his ears to listen, he heard a faint voice saying, \"Welcome to Subcon, the land of dreams. We have been cursed by Wart and we are completely under his evil spell. We have been awaiting your arrival. Please defeat Wart and return Subcon to its natural state. The curse Wart has put on you in the real world will not have any effect upon you here. Remember, Wart hates vegetables. Please help us!\"\n\nAt the same time this was heard, a bolt of lightning flashed before Mario’s eyes. Stunned, Mario lost his footing and tumbled upside down. He awoke with a start to find himself sitting up in his bed. To clear his head, Mario talked to Luigi, Toad and Princess Peach about the strange dream he had. They decided to go to a nearby mountain for a picnic.\n\nAfter arriving at the picnic area and looking at the scenery, they see a small cave nearby. When they enter this cave, to their great surprise, there’s a stairway leading up, up and up. It is exactly like the one Mario saw in his dream. They all walk together up the stairs and at the top, find a door just like the one in Mario’s dream. When Mario and his friends, in fear, open the door, to their surprise, the world that he saw in his dream spreads out before them!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
    {
